# AskUI Credentials
# Get your workspace ID and access token from the AskUI Portal:
# 1. Go to https://hub.askui.com and sign in
# 2. Navigate to Access Tokens in the sidebar
# 3. Create a new access token (see https://docs.askui.com/02-how-to-guides/01-account-management/04-tokens#create-access-token)
# 4. Copy the workspace ID and token below

ASKUI_WORKSPACE_ID=<your-workspace-id-here>
ASKUI_TOKEN=<your-token-here>
